{"tid":2295571,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"兩個人相處要知己知彼，原來真係好痛。求解讀","createTime":"2020-11-22T01:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T01:59:40.000Z","uid":65139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0926719e8cb37d78eb3fcbade762aebda03ec72a","tid":2295571,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">呢兩個人就係<br />\n我地同埋另一個國家嘅意識形態</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n發覺呢時候要試下解讀(even只係睇topic)另一個意識形態嘅論述真係好困難好痛苦<br />\n要睇一班有話語權嘅人(?)用一個痴撚線嘅語境講我自己的確係好嬲，而無力感又會令人心如刀割<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但當嬲同痛，而大家趨向選擇活響大紀元/新唐人嘅世界<br />\n<span class=\"large\">（dllm好多post都係quote佢地，入到見大家都已經射哂精）</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者連登呢個充滿Mon po狗/PR/1毛嘅Comfort Zone (still comfort?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n好快呢個香港浪潮/網絡力量都會變成圍爐<br />\n自己邊緣化自己，以為連登就係世界<br />\n<br />\n變成<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>做公關冇公關，做運動冇掙扎</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係唔打落去...<br />\n其實廢噏咗咁耐<br />\n其實都係想介紹大家睇下面「端」呢篇文<br />\n（copy咗少少，高質謀體課金穩陣，利伸：打手）<br />\n<br />\n講一個大陸好紅受眾好多嘅KOL - 兔主席<br />\n點向牆入面描繪香港呢場運動<br />\nshape大陸人對香港運動嘅果種不屑同側目<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">佢係LVL 99 PR 風向撚<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訂咗端/有心睇嘅好想知你地睇完點諗<br />\n留少少comment<br />\n麻煩都留一個負皮屌我傻鳩，然後上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅三代KOL兔主席的香港論述，為何在簡體輿論圈走紅？｜香港｜評論｜深度｜端傳媒 Initium Media <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20201117-hongkong-pro-beijing-camp-ren-yi-kol-mainland/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20201117-hongkong-pro-beijing-camp-ren-yi-kol-mainland%2F&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=ca47640b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20201117-hongkong-pro-beijing-camp-ren-yi-kol-mainland/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97uw8D8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97uw8D8.png&h=922b85de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a7222cdcf341b1f7f43290dcfa39e5bcdd2c128","tid":2295571,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zuCVQSU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzuCVQSU.png&h=6099058f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/czqTCxU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczqTCxU.png&h=0c8c4f67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fnfkhxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfnfkhxV.png&h=06b1a92b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gotaEMg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgotaEMg.png&h=d3c6e421&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9384d34125c0579798082d5999ff1614c81452cf","tid":2295571,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}